channel.description:
This channel was created to inspire people to stand up for their rights, to get involved in political activism and to become aware of what we stand to lose if we remain silent or ignorant. The people who wish to trample on our Bill of Rights and Constitution are very organized and good at what they do. In order for us to stand a chance, we must stand together. 

This channel will eventually become an alternative media outlet. I want to cover the news the media won't! I will being doing political commentary and news. I will be making educational videos on many topics such as our Constitution, the Patriot Act and the National Defense Authorization Act. I will be talking about topics such as emergency preparedness and much more! Please remember to subscribe and don't forget to comment/like/share my videos!

Know your rights! Assert your rights! Get On The Move!
